graph TD
    A[NGO Signs Up] --> B[Fill Organization Information]
    B --> C[Complete KYC Verification]
    C --> D{KYC Approved?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Account Created & Activated]
    D -->|No| F[Request Additional Information]
    F --> C
    E --> G[Access NGO Dashboard]

    G --> H[Browse Available Opportunities]
    H --> I{Receive Notifications?}
    I -->|New Brief Matching Profile| J[Notification Received]
    I -->|Browsing Dashboard| K[View Available Briefs]
    J --> K

    K --> L[View Brief Details]
    L --> M[Review Project Scope]
    M --> N[Check Budget & Milestones]
    N --> O{Interested to Apply?}
    O -->|No| K
    O -->|Yes| P[Submit Application]

    P --> Q[Provide Proposal]
    Q --> R[Detail Implementation Plan]
    R --> S[Highlight Team Expertise]
    S --> T[Submit Application to Donor]
    T --> U[Status: Pending Review]
    U --> UM{Message Donor?}
    UM -->|Yes| UMN[Open Messaging<br/>with Donor]
    UMN --> UMO[Discuss Application<br/>& Answer Questions]
    UMO --> U
    UM -->|No| V

    U --> V{Donor Decision?}
    V -->|Rejected| W[Application Rejected]
    W --> X[View Feedback from Donor]
    X --> XM{Message Donor<br/>for Feedback?}
    XM -->|Yes| XMN[Send Message]
    XMN --> XMO[Discuss Rejection Reasons]
    XMO --> Y
    XM -->|No| Y
    Y --> Y{Apply to Another Brief?}
    Y -->|Yes| K
    Y -->|No| Z[End]

    V -->|Approved| AA[Application Approved]
    AA --> AB[Congratulations: Partner Selected]
    AB --> ABM{Message Donor?}
    ABM -->|Yes| ABMN[Open Messaging<br/>with Donor]
    ABMN --> ABMO[Discuss Project Start<br/>& Requirements]
    ABMO --> AC
    ABM -->|No| AC
    AC --> AC[Receive 30percent Budget for Mobilization]
    AC --> AD[Budget Received in NGO Wallet]
    AD --> AE[Project Officially Started]

    AE --> AF[Access Project Management Hub]
    AF --> AG[View Milestones & Targets]
    AG --> AH[Begin Working on Project]
    AH --> AI[Milestone Updates Process]

    AI --> AJ[NGO Prepares Milestone Update]
    AJ --> AJ2[Upload Documentation &<br/>Images/Evidence]
    AJ2 --> AJ3[Write Detailed Description<br/>of Work Completed]
    AJ3 --> AJ4[Update Target Amount<br/>Percentage Covered]
    AJ4 --> AN[Submit Milestone Update<br/>to Donor]
    AN --> AO[Status: Pending<br/>Donor Verification]

    AO --> AP{Donor Reviews &<br/>Verifies Milestone}
    
    AP -->|APPROVED| AQ[✅ Milestone Verified<br/>& Approved]
    AQ --> AQP[💰 Payment Released<br/>to NGO Wallet]
    AQP --> AQP2{More Milestones<br/>Remaining?}
    AQP2 -->|Yes| AQP3[Start Next<br/>Milestone Work]
    AQP3 --> AI
    AQP2 -->|No| DONOR_MARK["🔔 Notify Donor:<br/>All Milestones Complete"]

    AP -->|REJECTED| AR[❌ Milestone Rejected]
    AR --> ARX[Project Ended<br/>No Further Payment]
    ARX --> AU[End Project]

    AP -->|NEEDS REVISION| ARA[Request Changes<br/>from NGO]
    ARA --> ARM{Message Donor<br/>for Clarification?}
    ARM -->|Yes| ARMN[Open Messaging<br/>with Donor]
    ARMN --> ARMO[Discuss Required Changes]
    ARMO --> ARM2{Understand<br/>Requirements?}
    ARM2 -->|Yes| AN
    ARM2 -->|No| ARMN
    ARM -->|No| AN
    
    DONOR_MARK --> AX[Donor Reviews Final<br/>Project Report]
    AX --> AXM{Donor Marks<br/>Project as<br/>Complete?}
    AXM -->|Yes| AXC[Project Marked<br/>as COMPLETED]
    AXM -->|No| AXH[Reopen for<br/>Additional Work]
    AXH --> AI
    
    AXC --> AY[Final Project Report<br/>Generated]
    AY --> AZ[View Project<br/>Impact Summary]
    AZ --> BA[Receive Project<br/>Completion Certificate]
    BA --> BB[Project Successfully<br/>Completed]
    BB --> BC[End]

